room_title: Escape room "Mission: Space" by Amazing Escape Room in New York
room_address: 585 N. Gannon Ave Staten Island, NY 10314
room_description: Something malfunctioned and your space ship went way off course! Now barreling through space without any sort of power, you and your team must find a way to power up your ship and get back to charted territory before things start to get worse! You only have 60 minutes to get the power on and return home or you will run out of oxygen. Can you get home?
